  "text": "The challenge at this point is to discriminate between direct effects of circadian clock disruption and indirect effects due to life style as a consequence of shift work itself [CITATION_1] , since for example a connection between night shift work and metabolic syndrome was also shown [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
